         MACRO
&NAME    TCOPMSG &TEXT,&REG=6
         LCLA  &LNGTH                       INITIALIZE LENGTH TO 0
&LNGTH   SETA  K'&TEXT-2                    COUNT CHAR IN MSG
&NAME    MVC   0(2,&REG),=AL2(&LNGTH+8)     MOVE TOTAL LENGTH TO OP MSG
         MVC   2(3,&REG),=X'020015'         MOVE START CHAR TO OP MSG
         MVC   5(&LNGTH,&REG),=C&TEXT       MOVE TEXT TO OP MSG
         MVC   &LNGTH+5(3,&REG),=X'150337'  MOVE EOT CHAR TO OP MSG
         MEND
